{"tid":300872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路牌、慶回歸橫額驚現「香港淪陷20年」塗鴉　fb專頁稱控訴港被中共控制","createTime":"2017-06-28T08:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T08:43:30.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9cf1eff6d7315173d4ae5f89418f88806e973b9","tid":300872,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/28/164245_6e2fd9a35679bf62da0e1b9603796a8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F28%2F164245_6e2fd9a35679bf62da0e1b9603796a8a.jpg&h=e7d3f1b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n回歸20周年在即，國家主席習近平明午來港。網上流傳相片，顯示「鴨寮街」路牌被寫上「香港淪陷20年」塗鴉，聲稱控訴香港在主權移交後，完全被中共控制。<br />\n<br />\n相片由facebook專頁「塗鴉少年 Street Art Boy」上載，相片顯示「鴨寮街」、「花園街」路牌被寫上「香港淪陷20年」塗鴉，亦有道路指示牌及慶回歸橫額被印上同款塗鴉字眼。<br />\n<br />\n專頁稱相片由其他網民提供，相信於兩天前拍攝。專頁又說，這行動欲控訴香港在主權移交後，完全被中共控制，「不是回歸是淪陷」。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》正向路政署查詢事件。翻查資料，路牌屬政府財物，塗鴉或破壞路牌可能要負上刑責。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170628/s00001/1498637869920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170628%2Fs00001%2F1498637869920&d=tJKTVhLpRLuiBczOP7vF00%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=944d8039\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170628%2Fs00001%2F1498637869920&h=55007852\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170628/s00001/1498637869920</a>"}]}